item.title: Why are Sexual Boundaries Critical for a truly "Connected Coupleship"?
item.description:
Once an addict starts into recovery and his partner begins her journey of healing betrayal trauma, a couple should immediately look at the difficult but essential work of SETTING BOUNDARIES. Why? Because the most connected relationships are BOUNDARIED RELATIONSHIPS! 

The first priority is to set boundaries that create "safety" in the relationship. Without safety, what every couple desires—intimacy (into-me-you-see)—is not possible... Feed: https://feeds.buzzsprout.com/813260.rss
